name: A second piece of galaxy
description:
Printable file of my artwork "A second piece of galaxy" from 2008, a very productive year for me. Much inspired by Egypt culture and particularly  the Sfinx. 
Drawing by hand, scanned into the computer and then started painting digitally.
7000 x 5252 pixels @ 300 dpi.
And, when desired, the buyer can get even a bigger size (double size) from me to print at HQ in 120 x 90 cm, 300 dpi.
